WEBVTT

00:02.339 --> 00:03.357
It's so dark.

00:03.358 --> 00:05.175
All new border agents
start out on night duty.

00:05.260 --> 00:06.293
Get used to it.

00:06.344 --> 00:07.728
Everything up past that rock
is Canada.

00:07.795 --> 00:08.979
That's all you got to know.

00:09.064 --> 00:10.514
Unless you forget
your long johns,

00:10.598 --> 00:11.682
it's a piece of cake.

00:11.766 --> 00:13.350
What about smugglers
or terrorists?

00:13.435 --> 00:14.801
This ain't Mexico, bucko.

00:14.853 --> 00:16.737
At most you'll get
a Mohawk slicking beer

00:16.804 --> 00:18.305
across the border
to avoid taxes.

00:19.157 --> 00:22.142
Where do they get you trainees?

00:22.193 --> 00:24.411
You can't even walk without
tripping over your own feet.

00:24.479 --> 00:25.662
Those aren't my feet!

00:29.584 --> 00:31.034
Oh, crap.

00:34.839 --> 00:36.540
This is gonna be
a lot of paperwork.

00:40.845 --> 00:42.296
Hey.

00:42.347 --> 00:43.497
What's wrong?

00:43.548 --> 00:44.765
Nothing.

00:44.832 --> 00:46.717
It's just, I received

00:46.801 --> 00:48.519
this letter of acceptance
from Columbia.

00:48.603 --> 00:49.887
Ooh, congratulations.

00:49.971 --> 00:51.054
In what?

00:51.139 --> 00:52.189
Undergraduate French literature.

00:52.273 --> 00:53.190
Are you telling me

00:53.274 --> 00:54.525
in some roundabout way

00:54.609 --> 00:56.326
that you want to radically
change your life?

00:56.394 --> 00:57.644
Yes.

00:57.695 --> 00:59.846
I'm also changing my name
to Michelle Welton.

00:59.898 --> 01:01.782
Oh, my God.

01:01.849 --> 01:04.233
Cam's daughter
got into Columbia.

01:04.319 --> 01:05.569
Yep.

01:05.653 --> 01:06.987
Wait, why did you open her mail?

01:07.038 --> 01:11.542
It was in my pile,
because Cam had it sent here.

01:11.626 --> 01:12.876
Cam?

01:12.961 --> 01:14.077
Wouldn't Michelle
give her address

01:14.145 --> 01:16.046
so that it would
just go right to...?

01:18.333 --> 01:21.602
Cam got her daughter
into Columbia behind her back.

01:21.669 --> 01:22.719
Because she didn't want her

01:22.804 --> 01:24.588
to go to that little school
up in Maine.

01:24.672 --> 01:25.839
Oh, wow.

01:25.890 --> 01:27.474
Honey, this is bad parenting.

01:27.542 --> 01:30.194
We will never do anything
like this, promise me now.

01:30.261 --> 01:31.378
What do I do now?

01:31.429 --> 01:33.013
You give it to Cam.

01:33.064 --> 01:34.047
I mean, do I say anything?

01:34.098 --> 01:36.049
No. It is not your business.

01:36.117 --> 01:37.684
Can I give her
a disapproving look?

01:37.735 --> 01:39.153
Of course.

01:40.188 --> 01:42.739
That's a good one.

01:45.393 --> 01:48.562
What's this?

01:48.613 --> 01:50.080
Oh.

01:52.584 --> 01:54.918
You have something to say
about this?

01:55.003 --> 01:57.571
Angela says no.

01:57.622 --> 01:59.206
But this is a disapproving look.

01:59.257 --> 02:00.290
Does it mean anything

02:00.375 --> 02:01.741
that it's all moot?

02:01.793 --> 02:03.910
Michelle is determined
to go to community college

02:03.962 --> 02:06.763
in outer Mongolia
to be with her boyfriend.

